  <summary>1/24/2005--Introduced.
Amends the Internal Revenue Code to authorize the issuance of tax-exempt facility bonds for certain highway and surface freight transfer facilities. Limits the amount of bonds that may be issued to $15 billion. Exempts such bonds from certain volume caps applicable to State issuers of private activity bonds.</summary>
